{"tid":2452674,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：邁克爾涉危害中國國安案在丹東開庭　使館人員被拒旁聽","createTime":"2021-03-19T03:39:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T03:43:43.000Z","uid":290404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dbcc658980fa79fb2ad2cd7311ed64ee288448ef","tid":2452674,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:39:29.000Z","msg":"<strong>加拿大商人邁克爾涉嫌危害中國國家安全犯罪的案件，早上在遼寧省丹東市中級人民法院進行首次審訊。</strong>一名加拿大駐華使館高級官員向路透社透露，自己被禁止進入法院旁聽，對審訊缺乏透明度感到失望。<br />\n<br />\n內地警方在法院外設置封鎖線，早上9時有警車護送法院車輛進入法院範圍。<br />\n<br />\n邁克爾與另一名涉嫌危害中國國家安全的加拿大前外交官康明凱，在2018年12月起被扣押至今。報道說，康明凱的審訊將於下星期一在北京進行。外交部強調，審訊時間與剛進行的中美對話無任何關係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581438-20210319.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581438-20210319.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSqVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=724f61de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581438-20210319.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8fcc50da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581438-20210319.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"7acaa8f7467d94659309c364801962a8cb1ec16f","tid":2452674,"uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d5e78c55a8e95a15c8db5f583e718e3d723cf3","tid":2452674,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:42:31.000Z","msg":"中共：罪無可恕，判處死刑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DUWo23N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDUWo23N.jpg&h=d56ce7e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90b964e6d13c9a87fca3e10b824b4a94ebd59953","tid":2452674,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:42:33.000Z","msg":"外交部強調，審訊時間與剛進行的中美對話無任何關係。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3f506aa7e2ae1255a27b2fe9a6906edc6bb6f5","tid":2452674,"uid":304935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbcc658980fa79fb2ad2cd7311ed64ee288448ef","tid":2452674,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:39:29.000Z","msg":"<strong>加拿大商人邁克爾涉嫌危害中國國家安全犯罪的案件，早上在遼寧省丹東市中級人民法院進行首次審訊。</strong>一名加拿大駐華使館高級官員向路透社透露，自己被禁止進入法院旁聽，對審訊缺乏透明度感到失望。<br />\n<br />\n內地警方在法院外設置封鎖線，早上9時有警車護送法院車輛進入法院範圍。<br />\n<br />\n邁克爾與另一名涉嫌危害中國國家安全的加拿大前外交官康明凱，在2018年12月起被扣押至今。報道說，康明凱的審訊將於下星期一在北京進行。外交部強調，審訊時間與剛進行的中美對話無任何關係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581438-20210319.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581438-20210319.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSqVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=724f61de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581438-20210319.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8fcc50da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581438-20210319.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:43:43.000Z","msg":"ALM: 支持中國"}]}